&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://url=http://www.scarleteen.com/article/etc/to_be_awesome_or_just_be_––_tips_on_making_the_most_of_your_life_right_now&quot;&gt;To Be... AWESOME or Just Be –– Tips on Making the Most of Your Life Right Now!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scarleteen.com/article/bodies/life_lessons_from_the_third_stall_on_the_left&quot;&gt;Life Lessons from the Third Stall on the Left&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em&gt;(This one&#039;s seriously from the archives: it&#039;s one of the oldest pieces here!)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
