&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scarleteen.com/blog/heather_corinna/2011/11/10/losers_can_be_awesome_a_lesson_brought_to_you_by_the_chicago_cubs&quot;&gt;Losers Can Be Awesome: a Lesson Brought to You by the Chicago Cubs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
