&lt;li&gt;Control: Janet Jackson&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play It Right: Sylvan Esso&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Motion Says: Arthur Russell&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Talking Loud and Clear: Orchestral Manoeuvres In the Dark&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Kiss Is Not a Contract: Flight of the Conchords&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don&#039;t Touch My Hair (feat. Sampha) : Solange&lt;/li&gt;
